вҚқ Structured_variable.tc

      PERSON.firstname вҶҗ 'Jane'   вҚқ creates PERSON with member 'firstname'
      PERSON.lastname  вҶҗ 'Doe'    вҚқ add a second member 'lastname' to PERSON

      PERSON.address.city   вҶҗ  'Berkeley 94704'     вҚқ also does PERSON.address
      PERSON.address.street вҶҗ  '42 Shattuck Ave.'   вҚқ also does PERSON.address

      )ERASE PERSON.address

      PERSON.address.city   вҶҗ  'Berkeley 94704'     вҚқ refresh
      PERSON.address.street вҶҗ  '42 Shattuck Ave.'   вҚқ refresh
      PERSON.address.street вҶҗ  '44 Shattuck Ave.'   вҚқ override

      PERSON.address.street
44 Shattuck Ave.

