      )ERASE A C
      A.b.cвҶҗ'leaf-Abc'        вҚқ OK, since a.b.c will be a leaf
      A.bвҶҗ42                  вҚқ will fail since a.b is not a leaf
DOMAIN ERROR+
      A.bвҶҗ42
