      )MORE
member access: cannot override non-leaf member A.b
      )ERASE or вҺ•EX that member first.

      )ERASE A.b
      A.b вҶҗ 'leaf-Ab'         вҚқ now OK, since A.b will now be a leaf

      )SIC
      )ERASE A
      A.b.c вҶҗ 'leaf-Abc'      вҚқ variable A with leaf A.b.C
      C.d.e вҶҗ 'leaf-Cde'      вҚқ variable C with leaf C.d.e
      A.b.c вҶҗ C               вҚқ override A.b.c
      A.b.c.d.e
leaf-Cde

      (вҶ‘A.b)вҶҗ2
DOMAIN ERROR+
      (вҶ‘A.b)вҶҗ2
         ^  ^
      )more
member access: cannot use non-leaf member A.b in selective specification.
      )ERASE or вҺ•EX that member first.
      )SIC

