      RвҶҗ39 вҺ•CR W
R
 bb leaf-bb 
 a  leaf-a  

      вҚқ 38 вҺ•CR turns scalar chars in Q into 1-element vector chars in W
      R1вҶҗR[вҚӢR[;1];]   вҚқ R1 is R with member names sorted
      R1 вүЎ (,ВЁQ)
